<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fluvial processes primarily disturb stands rather than fire. Fires are not common, though fire frequency and character can be associated with neighboring upland alliances. Plants are top-killed by low- and moderate-intensity fire, and they sprout vigorously after disturbance.</div>
